      },
      {
        "name": "Hooves",
        "text": "*Melee Weapon Attack:* atk[str] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. *Hit:* dmg[2d10 + str] bludgeoning damage."
      },
      {
        "name": "Petrifying Breath (Recharge 5-6)",
        "text": "[name] exhales petrifying gas in a 30-foot cone. Each creature in that area must succeed on a DC 13 Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, a target begins to turn to stone and is restrained. The restrained target must repeat the saving throw at the end of its next turn. On a success, the effect ends on the target. On a failure, the target is petrified until freed by the greater restoration spell or other magic."
      }
    ]
  },
